description_content_original:
Features:
1.Characteristics: the eye mask outline border equipped with ventilation system, increase the air running circulation and comfortable.
2.Wear: advanced design conforms to the all kinds of helmet, gun sights, telescopes, night vision system etc. Frame designed tough, light and easy matched with anybody's face feature.
3.Test: resistance to impact lens, beyond US standard ANSI Z87.1 level 1 impact resistance standard.
4.Lens: lens imported POLYCARBONATE strengthen the lens.
5.Suit for cloudy day and have good anti-fog, anti-impact, anti-scratch and 100% anti-UV function.
 
Descriptions:
1.Optically correct clear lens which is durable and shatter-proof
2.Around frame with high density black sponge protect your face.
 
Specifications:
Condition: Brand New
Lens Color: Yellow, White, Gray
Frame Color: black&gray ,black&yellow,black&white,black&pink
Material: Plastic
Size:145*145*41mm
Fitment:Fit for motorcycle, skiing, snowboard, scooter and outdoor sports.
 
Package Included:
1 x Motorcycle Goggle
 
Notes:
1.Due to the difference between different monitors, the picture may not reflect the actual color of the item. We guarantee the style is the same as shown in the pictures.
